{"tid":265030,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻鼠佢塊面同耳仔做咩事?","createTime":"2017-05-31T10:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T16:57:45.000Z","uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc8f2c9185c2eafb83b3a20e61e379462aea33eb","tid":265030,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的,<br />\n半個月前我發現自己隻鼠個耳仔生左野,咁我都開post問過巴絲們係咩黎.<br />\n咁點知岩岩拎上手,見到佢塊面紅紅地,點知又係生呢啲野,<br />\n我想問點解會咁,關唔關佢啲糧入面有瓜子事?<br />\n補返圖.<br />\n半個月前:<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/au6d8hsy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fau6d8hsy&h=ab3801c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fg4xu17r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffg4xu17r&h=d0957d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r7uf3dmc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr7uf3dmc&h=36e846b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日:<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pm2hlfo6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpm2hlfo6&h=718d01a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5tf07vkx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5tf07vkx&h=081bd036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a634991cac37658baa4249d11651e1ad266c28a","tid":265030,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e5fed905d5e280c774bec79d625909e26b6d2e","tid":265030,"uid":11846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"聽朋友講如果食太多瓜子有機會生cancer<br />\n利申：聽返黎，唔知真定假"},{"pid":"d8a852ed384659ca515f2eeeb47f509b72539630","tid":265030,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽朋友講如果食太多瓜子有機會生cancer<br />\n利申：聽返黎，唔知真定假</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615d970bd28d9a27f3aa43c8e7e4d163e6349a4b","tid":265030,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽朋友講如果食太多瓜子有機會生cancer<br />\n利申：聽返黎，唔知真定假</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我餵開嗰隻糧有唔少瓜子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77e3f10a356f39e8b68750e2d25649b2ef25e98","tid":265030,"uid":16032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"瓜子係倉鼠界既薯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾少啲啦，勁熱氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a5a3ed34895a8b08ef149b719733d375ab3eca","tid":265030,"uid":3344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瓜子係倉鼠界既薯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾少啲啦，勁熱氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉,早知係咁就唔餵咁多,咁我而家除左減走佢啲瓜子之外,仲有咩可以做到?"},{"pid":"e6432a6d1a46caf69b77ffb1f1804f8ed28bd34f","tid":265030,"uid":16032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>瓜子係倉鼠界既薯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾少啲啦，勁熱氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉,早知係咁就唔餵咁多,咁我而家除左減走佢啲瓜子之外,仲有咩可以做到?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你知啲鼠一日可以柯成廿幾粒屎架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲屎會有細菌，所以最重要係日日都要清潔個籠<br />\n最好一個星期用熱用洗一次啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n衛生啲就ok"},{"pid"